node.text: Good morning, everyone! I am happy to announce that my first book is available for purchase wherever books are sold right now: Amazon, Barnes & Noble, Walmart, Target….everywhere so get your copy today. It’s a children’s book called “Chandler” who was a dog that I had for 18 years. When he died, it really broke my heart, so I wrote this book to help me deal with the pain. This book has helped keep Chandler’s memory alive and it serves as a healing tool for others dealing with the loss of someone special. I hope you enjoy it, too. Thank you @kimbercon711. #newbooks #childrensbooks #authorsofinstagram #authorssupportingauthors
